<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV15">
<l>aṅkamāṟum vētanāṉku mākiniṉṟa vaṟṟuḷē</l>
<l>taṅkukiṉṟa taṉmaiyāyta ṭaṅkaṭaṟpa ṇattalaic</l>
<l>ceṅkaṇāka ṇaikkiṭanta celvamalku cīriṉāy</l>
<l>caṅkavaṇṇa maṉṉamēṉi cārṅkapāṇi yallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Becoming the six [Vedic] components and the four Vedas</l>
<l>O You whose nature consists in being established in those!</l>
<l>O You with the excellence of abounding wealth</l>
<l>who recline on the bed that is the snake with red eyes at the top of the hoods,</l>
<l rend="indent">upon the wide ocean!</l>
<l>Are you not the Śārṅga-Holder with a body akin to the hue of the conch?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
